Total’s Ghanaian Unit Appoints Guillaume Larroque as Its Managing Director

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-31T04:50:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/total-s-ghanaian-unit-appoints-guillaume-larroque-as-its-managing-director.html
Total SA’s Ghanaian unit,  Total
Petroleum Ghana Ltd. (TOTAL) , apppointed Guillaume Larroque as managing
director, replacing Jonathan Molapo, the fuel retailer said in a
statement published on the website of the Ghana Stock Exchange
dated Aug. 29.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  